\sqrt{\frac{2}{\pi}}
\frac{2^{n+2}(n+2)!\cdot 2^n n!}{(2n+4)!} = \frac{2^{2n+2}}{\binom{2n+2}{n}}\cdot \frac{1}{(2n+3)(2n+4)}.
\frac{1}{2^{2n+2}}\binom{2n+2}{n} \sim \frac{1}{\sqrt{\pi n}},
O(n^{-3/2})
1-x\leq e^{-x}
x\geq \log(1+x)
\frac{(2n)!!}{(2n+3)!!}=\prod_{k=1}^n\left(1-\frac{3}{2k+3}\right)\leq\exp\left(-\sum_{k=1}^{n}\frac{3}{2k+3}\right)\leq\exp\left(-\frac{3}{2}\sum_{k=3}^{n+2}\frac{1}{k}\right)\leq\exp\left(-\frac{3}{2}\sum_{k=3}^{n+2}\log\frac{k+1}{k}\right)=\left(\prod_{k=3}^{n+2}\frac{k+1}{k}\right)^{-3/2}=\left(\frac{n+3}{3}\right)^{-3/2}<6\cdot n^{-3/2}
